high_descs: walk straight to wooden table, stop in front of wooden table
pick up ladle with black handle from wooden table
turn right, walk to kitchen sink, stop at sink
put ladle into kitchen sink basin, wash with water, pick up ladle
turn around and walk to wooden table, stop in front of wooden table
put ladle on table to the right of the loaf of bread
anns.task_desc: get ladle, wash it, return it to wooden table

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right again to go to the table.
Pick up the spoon on the table, to the left of the apple.
Turn right, and go to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Return to the table behind you.
Place the spoon on the table to the right of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and go back to the brown table.
Pick up the laddle from the front of the table.
Take the laddle and go to the right, over to the counter with the tomato.
Place the laddle in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the laddle again.
Carry the laddle and turn around. Go to the brown table across the room on the right.
Place the laddle on the table, to the right of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a laddle and move it to the table.
